                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden"> You&#039;re not doomed just because you have a desk job. Here&#039;s how to fix the all-too-common problem.</div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2015-11-25"
>
  November 25, 2015  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
       <span><a
          href="http://greatist.com/p/amyeisinger"
          title="User profile of "
          class="username"
          about="http://greatist.com/p/amyeisinger"
          typeof="sioc:UserAccount"
          itemprop="url"
